comments: Ingles (UTA) legally contest Wiggins' (GSW) shot attempt.
Bazemore (GSW) makes contact with Clarkson's (UTA) backside during his driving shot attempt.
Clarkson (UTA) swipes to contest the shot but does not make contact with Bazemore's (GSW) arm during his shot attempt.
As O'Neale (UTA) begins to roll, he makes marginal contact with Wiggins (GSW) during the pick.
Bazemore (GSW) legally contests Clarkson's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) makes marginal contact with O'Neale (UTA) as the pick concludes.
Curry (GSW) makes marginal contact with Clarkson's (UTA) off-arm as he dribbles.
Curry (GSW) makes contact with Clarkson's (UTA) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a legal picking position in O'Neale's (UTA) path and does not deliver any contact.
Bogdanovic (UTA) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Looney (GSW) makes marginal contact with Gobert's (UTA) hand during the rebound.
O'Neale (UTA) legally contests Curry's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Looney (GSW) makes marginal contact with Clarkson's (UTA) body as they meet after the release of Clarkson's driving shot attempt.
As Poole (GSW) moves off ball, he dislodges Clarkson (UTA) during the inbounds play.
O'Neale (UTA) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Niang (UTA) briefly places an arm around Green (GSW) and makes marginal contact with Green as they move in the same path during the inbound play.
Bazemore (GSW) legally contests Clarkson's (UTA) jump shot attempt.
Green (GSW) clamps Gobert's (UTA) arm and restricts his ability to rebound.

Bogdanovic (UTA) makes contact with the ball and it remains in bounds near the baseline.  Green (GSW) plants his left foot in bounds and lifts his right foot off of the floor, establishing himself in bounds, and then makes contact with the ball and it never goes out of bounds.
